platforms		darwin
description		Ruby/GnomePrint is a Ruby binding of libgnomeprint.
long_description	Ruby/GnomePrint is a Ruby binding of libgnomeprint.
categories-append	gnome
license			LGPLv2
checksums		md5 40451e4173e2c8bcd5046aea7e499ef9 \
